              <div style="background:#0d0d1a;border-left:3px solid #f472b6;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0">
                <span style="color:#f9a8d4;font-weight:700">3. Projeto</span>
                <code style="margin-left:.6rem;font-size:.74rem">brandspace/CLAUDE.md, ralab/CLAUDE.md…</code>
                <span style="float:right;font-size:.72rem;color:#4b5563">injetado via buildFullContext() no prompt + carregado se cwd = projeto</span>
              </div>
